All the source code of RetroRocket is released under the terms of the
GNU General Public License version 3, as published by the Free
Software Foundation.  See the file gpl.txt for the full license text
or visit <http://www.gnu.org/licenses/>

The game music (Cruising in Space) is released under the terms of the
Creative Commons by-nc-nd license.  See the file cc_by-nc-nd.txt for
the full license or visit <http://creativecommons.org/>

Game graphics for the original TurboRaketti games and the original
TurboRaketti sounds are taken directly from the original TurboRaketti
II game which was released as freeware by Heikki Kosola in 1998.

Game graphics for the original Thrust levels are loosely based on the
graphics from the GPL thrust for Linux.

The binary file (retrorocket.nds) is linked against the following
libraries: 
 - libfat
 - libnds
 - mikmod (LGPL)
 - liblobby (unknown license)
 - PAlib

For all other files, the GPL V3 applies.

